---
title: Beef and Pepper Skewers with Zucchini and Couscous Salad
description: Using skewers to alternate meat with veggies is a genius way to sneak colorful foods into those little tummies. In this recipe, we’ve paired beef with peppers and tossed together a citrusy couscous salad to round it all out. Feel free to use the broiler or the grill for this recipe — up to you!
